define root view entity yeho_ddl_I_Bankpass

{
  key companycode       as Companycode,
  key glaccount         as Glaccount,
  key currency          as Currency,
  key bankaccount       as Bankaccount,

      bank_code         as BankCode,
      branch_code       as BranchCode,
      firm_code         as FirmCode,
      service_user      as ServiceUser,
      service_password  as ServicePassword,
      owner_title       as OwnerTitle,
      owner_description as OwnerDescription,
      suffix            as Suffix,
      connection_type   as ConnectionType,
      rfc_destination   as RfcDestination,
      service_url       as ServiceUrl,
      namespace_url     as NamespaceUrl,
      class_suffix      as ClassSuffix,
      cpi_user          as CpiUser,
      cpi_password      as CpiPassword,
      cpi_url           as CpiUrl,
      additional_field1 as AdditionalField1,
      additional_field2 as AdditionalField2,
      additional_field3 as AdditionalField3,
      class_name        as ClassName
}
